Verify you can write an extension that adds menu entries to the editor tab context menu that can do something with the resource that is being shown. This context menu also shows up when tabs are disabled and you right click on the editor title.

The related menu key for package.json is `editor/title/context`, e.g.:

``` json
"commands": [{
    "command": "doSomething",
    "title": "Do Something"
}],
"menus": {
    "editor/title/context": [
        {
            "command": "doSomething"
        }
    ]
}
```
